    <item>
      <title>美联储后亚洲股市上涨，日元恢复下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/asian-stocks-to-fall-yen-steadies-after-surge-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔淡化进一步加息的前景后，大多数亚洲股市上涨。日元在突然上涨（暗示官方干预）后恢复下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/asian-stocks-to-fall-yen-steadies-after-surge-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 23:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>星展银行首席执行官古普塔今年盈利超出预期，再创新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/dbs-profit-beats-estimates-on-higher-lending-wealth-fees-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星展集团控股有限公司首席执行官皮尤什·古普塔 (Piyush Gupta) 预计，由于强劲的贷款和理财费用，这家新加坡最大的银行取得了好于预期的业绩，今年将再创历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/dbs-profit-beats-estimates-on-higher-lending-wealth-fees-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
